external_knowledge:
- Sensor components refer to a specific type of component that provides sensory input to a system; 
- Input pins are pins on a component that receive input from other components or external sources; 
- The revision date refers to the date a revision was made to a component; 
- The username indicates the user who made the revision.

sql:
SELECT package_type, AVG(pin_count) AS average_pins
FROM packages
GROUP BY package_type;
